caption: I remember when I first found her on YouTube. I was watching her first video and thought "wow this girl is going places she's amazing!" When you hear her voice you get those chill bumps and the hair raises on your arms and you're left speechless. She was and still is the absolute best! I love you Christina Grimmie!! Thank you for amazing music and being the most amazing and caring person ever!! #RIPChristina #FlyHighBeautiful  ❤️🙏🏻👼🏼
song_album: The Complete Season 6 Collection (The Voice Performance)
